title: Salmon and spinach filo pouches
ingredients: ['2 tbsp soy sauce', '3 spring onions, trimmed and chopped', 'juice of 1 lime', '1 garlic clove, chopped', '2 tsp sesame seeds', '400g skinned fresh salmon fillet, cut into small cubes', '225g pack baby leaf spinach', '100g frozen minted peas, thawed', '4 sheets filo pastry, about 180g in total', '1 tbsp vegetable oil', '2 tsp sesame seed oil', '100g reduced-fat soft cheese']
